urlText: Trackwork between Glenfield and Sydenham
content:
Saturday 4 and Sunday 5 June
  • Buses replace trains between Glenfield and Sydenham.
  • T3 Bankstown and T4 Eastern Suburbs & Illawarra Line trains run between Sydenham and the City.
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between:
    • Macarthur and the City via Granville
    • Campbelltown and Central, platforms 1-12, via Regents Park
    • Turrella and the City via the Airport
  • If you are travelling to International Airport, Domestic Airport, Mascot or Green Square catch bus route 23T8 to Wolli Creek and change for a train.
